summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of the east 80 feet of the north 25 feet and the west 21 feet of the east 61 feet of the south 12.6 feet of the north 37.6 feet of Lot 7, and the east 80 feet of Lot 8, Block 16, Woodland Addition to Salmon Bay City, located on the southwest corner of Fremont Avenue and North 50th Street, with respect to Use District, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 2-19.
